 />\n諗下點解沙律得d菜賣三四廿蚊盒<br />\n諗下點解紙品要標榜係再造<br />\n諗下點解tesla賣貴過benz</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n力<br />\n心聲</blockquote><br />\n以前都仲會諗下，衣家真係睇化左<br />\n自從轉左份新工，屌佢每日d浪費紙張浪費電力跟本我鏗一年都補唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本由小市民入手跟本就錯方向，你一係就大企業入手，一係就真係極端d好似上面巴打咁諗人口清洗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6592ffe495399715c828df085486950703222f76","tid":452020,"uid":4559,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7353b67c8381eee711aa45615dc2d33cb1da15ae","tid":452020,"uid":4559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20101b727f6e8cef4396469c940c6fa85eca6a67","tid":452020,"uid":78546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:06:56.000Z","msg":"做過食肆（尤其係自助餐）<br />\n就知你一年唔食肉慳埋慳埋都唔夠餐廳一日倒個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae7a306f1da8c5120dcb0b4b028c9781e6f6621","tid":452020,"uid":96182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過食肆（尤其係自助餐）<br />\n就知你一年唔食肉慳埋慳埋都唔夠餐廳一日倒個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟本事實就係無論邊一方面ge環保都應該係由工業商業開始控制有排都未到小市民"},{"pid":"6ccb213543959b40317f69c4b037254a43f028fd","tid":452020,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:17:15.000Z","msg":"每天都要食牛肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牛肉差唔多係最好食嘅肉，又嫩又甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑牛，正到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b39bd7689b346b9ea12a73cb14c1e03073c4a04","tid":452020,"uid":47095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"人越大越覺得好多環保concept根本on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a5a179c43dd3b4f1d919cf38cc69e1c3b04c28","tid":452020,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"重點係全球人口太多<br />\n食物鏈以及生態系統根就維持唔到咁多人<br />\n所以食物鏈同生態系統會慢慢collapse 而global warming 係其中一個徵狀"},{"pid":"928a2a5c1d2755257ecfb38457e5221be60c7186","tid":452020,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人越大越覺得好多環保concept根本on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9未必, 但係好多都好surreal"},{"pid":"289f53e21645de6a6af8e915b71f19afa56cc661","tid":452020,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係有效既方法，係要人類既人口大規模降低，<br />\n<br />\n生活方式重大改變，<br />\n<br />\n其實人類依家有既科技已經可以維持我地係地球上生活既安全，<br />\n<br />\n食物唔可以再食咁多魚肉，將薯類、植物等等作為主要食糧，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">世界上我諗無一種物種好似人類咁成日要番工成日要做自己唔想做既野</span><br />\n<br />\n現今世界既發展方向到底係咪岩？</blockquote><br />\n你意思係非洲草原上既斑馬要過條佈滿鱷魚既河係佢自己想？<br />\n醒下啦 全世界  甚至你廚房隻小強每刻都係為生活而做啲佢唔想做既野 例如冒住比你老母拍死既風險去執啲廚餘食</blockquote><br />\nON撚鳩你諗野掉番轉黎諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35999a86abf9691ae5b877173c3312d54d5285ad","tid":452020,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人越大越覺得好多環保concept根本on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9未必, 但係好多都好surreal</blockquote><br />\n環保本身係一件好事 但係得你一個做根本冇用 唯有盡量可以做既就做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ea8ba21a9aa2026e92efaa740962d204a8d22a","tid":452020,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36347e369c5e8fef9d4415b247121f0b27f05cee","tid":452020,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:40:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"