mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拯救地球靠曬你啦</blockquote><br />\nOk 辛苦我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39762c2443032fcf1bc631447fa17a23f6bf635b","tid":452020,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f82339fff39e2405b85559344b88d7d732a8b350","tid":452020,"uid":136752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"樓上係咁話其他人/機構浪費 我地點慳都補唔返 <br />\n啱架 從來都係自己做好 就算知道幫助唔大 都做左自己份先"},{"pid":"a92bc809e2cbdb4dca33439ae7d9a004f9800d0e","tid":452020,"uid":136752,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"同埋樓上話菜一樣有生命嗰啲 人類要維持生命一定要食野 我當自己一餐食一碟菜 但係牛呢 碟菜既份量對牛黎講 頭盤都嫌棄少啦 所以食牛/動物真係會用多地球好多資源"},{"pid":"7701c61e4c6f75247b1db45da57228cb3d2ce2a8","tid":452020,"uid":127475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"環保真係要減少人類先治本，將來可能真係會實行國定殺戮日"},{"pid":"02fab4bd5fd20c654564b147a07a16f4d807ac1f","tid":452020,"uid":32473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"我都冇食好幾年<br />\n個人皮膚好左<br />\n冇咁燥"},{"pid":"ee8bf4e2ffb0e60ffbab3d11d3dc4ce0d032b921","tid":452020,"uid":67864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"過多幾十年我都要啦 關我撚事我咩 我又唔生仔"},{"pid":"f4f7784a24036c78d9fb7d5f73ac712f79a75c98","tid":452020,"uid":67864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多幾十年我都死啦 關我撚事我咩 我又唔生仔</blockquote>"},{"pid":"705a2aacb963276b9d138e20f53e73ac59074229","tid":452020,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post感慨萬分<br />\n今晚就去打邊爐喪隊牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf25ab77f95800e1fd342862be0345b432a0f3b","tid":452020,"uid":132289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:20:53.000Z","msg":"上面D人真係唔好生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ce87ff0fafe9fab2f4ecb278ff043998019b6f","tid":452020,"uid":132289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人越大越覺得好多環保concept根本on撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為你愈大愈on9囉傻西"},{"pid":"9e5989b38fbb8e421eabc3c26eac0b4ff39ea6d6","tid":452020,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"其實所有食物都有佢既營養 <br />\n人點都要吸收 <br />\n好似健身咁 你唔食肉何來長肉 <br />\n人就係要均衡飲食 你食少一樣野 就會多一樣病痛 <br />\n係 牛 豬 全部都好慘 <br />\n不過人就係基於自己既需求去食野 <br />\n你叫人戒既同時 有冇第樣野取代到牛肉既味道同營養？ <br />\n而且聽過好多素食者 比醫生建議定期要食紅肉 <br />\n我唔係針對素食者 而係的確冇咩肉類或者其他食物取代到牛肉咁豐富既營養"}]}